{
  "stem": "1338.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was another world history separately, or Polish history.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was religion.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was the Bible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Bible was separate.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Studying the Bible was a subject separate from religion.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then I had Latin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I had English for two years, until the Germans came and then we switched to German.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was an interesting story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I'll get to that, I presume, when we talk about the war itself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so I had two years of English before the war started and two years of Latin.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And two years of Latin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so it was a rich curriculum.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was very well done by very good teachers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Then, I went home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I don't remember the hours anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I would usually go with my friend.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I don't remember life when we were in our own apartment, vaguely only.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I remember the times were pretty bad, where we had one room or a room in the kitchen or whatever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And so I usually went to-- since most of my classmates were very, very rich, I mean, very prosperous, since the school was obviously meant for prosperous people, so I used to go to their home usually.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Vice versa, it did not happen, which was a source of a certain probably feeling of inferiorities.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But then again, a child has opportunity for some many inferiorities.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] At this point, I look at it, it's hard for me to reflect upon it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But I suspect that if you asked me to go back to those times, it probably hurt me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It probably was a problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] Then, I would go home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I would do homework either with my friends--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably, most of the time.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
